DESCRIPTION:Join us on Tuesday\, October 28\, from 4–8 PM at Whispering Vine Fourth Street for a remarkable evening featuring the legendary Shafer Vineyards\, one of Napa Valley’s most respected and consistently top-rated wineries. Enjoy a curated tasting of Shafer’s acclaimed portfolio alongside a fresh flatbread\, all hosted in a relaxed\, intimate setting.\nTasting Fee: $45 (Includes flatbread and tasting)\nFeatured Wines:\n• Shafer One Point Five Cabernet Sauvignon 2023 – 96 pts Jeb Dunnuck\, 94 pts Robert Parker’s Wine Advocate – Deeply structured and silky\, with cassis\, graphite\, and floral spice leading to a long\, velvety finish.\n• Shafer Relentless 2021 – 97 pts James Suckling\, 95 pts Vinous\, 94 pts Jeb Dunnuck – Bold and powerful with layers of dark fruit\, peppery spice\, and savory richness balanced by fine\, elegant tannins.\n• Shafer TD-9 Cabernet Sauvignon 2023 – 95 pts James Suckling\, 95 pts Jeb Dunnuck – Lush and expressive with black cherry\, raspberry\, and graphite woven into a beautifully balanced\, full-bodied frame.\n• Shafer Red Shoulder Ranch Chardonnay 2024 – Vivid and refined with white peach\, pear\, and citrus blossom over a bright\, mineral-driven finish.\nExperience the craftsmanship and legacy of Shafer Vineyards\, a Napa icon renowned for its precision\, power\, and elegance.
LOCATION:4201 W Fourth St Reno\, NV 89523
SUMMARY:Flights & Flatbread with Shafer Vineyards
